<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section name="79">
	<p>
		During the day, you undertake several wrestling bouts.
		<random dice="3">
			<adjust ability="combat" modifier="noweapon"/>
		</random>, and add your COMBAT rating (not including any item bonuses, obviously).
	</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="3-9">
			Lose <lose shards="50"/> and
			<lose stamina="1d">1-6 points of Stamina</lose>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="10-15">
			Lose <lose shards="25"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="16-17">
			Win <gain shards="25"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="18+">
			Win <gain shards="50"/>, lose
			<lose stamina="1d">1-6 points of Stamina</lose>
		</outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>When you are ready, you leave the bazaar. <goto section="444"/>.</p>
</section>
